tika.dc.description:
His princess in scrubs...

Dr. Kiki Fender knew when Prince Stefano of Aspelicus disappeared after their whirlwind affair that he was not the man who would give her a happy-ever-after. Even if she was the only woman who had infiltrated the steely barriers around his proud and dutiful heart.

But now they are doctors working together aboard a cruise ship, and Stefano realizes there's one duty that has completely eluded him - his duty to himself. If he wants Kiki to be his princess, he has to prove that he's her Prince Charming after all....
